milestones.description: French and Tim Smart's 44-run partnership is HKG's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 13 between French and Tim Smart
French and Tabarak Dar's 50-run partnership is HKG's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 23 between Tabarak Dar and Tim Smart
Manoj Cheruparambil and Afzaal Haider's 47-run partnership is HKG's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 29 between Sher Lama and Ilyas Gull
Manoj Cheruparambil and Khalid Khan's 7-run partnership is HKG's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 2 between Sher Lama and Afzaal Haider
Manoj Cheruparambil and Nadeem Ahmed's 9-run partnership is HKG's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 7 between Sher Lama and Khalid Khan
Afzaal Haider has conceded the most runs in an innings (73) in ODIs for HKG, going past French's record of 51
French and Tabarak Dar's 50-run partnership is HKG's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 29 between Ilyas Gull and Sher Lama
Tabarak Dar's 36 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for HKG), surpassing Tabarak Dar's 20
Tabarak Dar has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (24) in an innings in ODIs for HKG, going past Tabarak Dar's 8
French has broken the record for most catches (2) in ODIs for HKG, going past Najeeb Amar's 1
Afzaal Haider has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (2) for HKG, going past Manoj Cheruparambil
